## 🎯 What is AI-OppHub?

AI-OppHub is a full-stack web platform that helps Indian students, developers, and innovators discover and apply to **live hackathons, government grants, and fellowship programs** — with an AI assistant that scores your pitch before you submit.

### The Problem We Solve
> Rural and semi-urban innovators miss out on high-value opportunities because information is scattered across dozens of platforms, emails, and social media groups.

### Our Solution
✅ Aggregate live opportunities in one place (via Devfolio API)  
✅ AI-powered pitch coaching before you apply  
✅ WhatsApp-first alerts for low-bandwidth users  
✅ Personalized match scores for each opportunity  

